title: plis rito
body: Gold last season, 7win 3loss placement matches (vsing plats+ cause of duo queue/ trio queue). Gets placed in silver 2 HAHAHAHAHHAAHHAHA THATS SO HILARIOUS

replies.body: This happens every season, it's nothing new. Your mmr soft resets at new season start. If you were G5 and got placed S2 that's actually pretty good. G4-3 it'd be pretty normal for 7-3. If you were G1 it would suck but you didn't mention your actual div.
So just get back in gold... Simple...
I went 6-4. S4 at season end, dropped to S5 :/
xD you made me lol hard!!!!11
